text: Velika Lašna (; in older sources also Velika Lašina,Leksikon občin kraljestev in dežel zastopanih v državnem zboru, vol. 6: Kranjsko. 1906. Vienna: C. Kr. Dvorna in Državna Tiskarna, p. 26. ) is a small village in the hills south of the Tuhinj Valley in the Upper Carniola region of Slovenia. ==References== ==External links== *Velika Lašna at Geopedia * Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Kamnik
title: Velika Lašna
